- **Brain:** `useGemmaInference.js` uses Transformers.js `automatic-speech-recognition` (`Xenova/whisper-tiny.en`) and `summarization` (`Xenova/distilbart-cnn-6-6`), with WebGPU → WASM fallback. Model IDs live in `src/brain/brainModels.js` for a future swap to Gemma 4 E2B when supported.
- **Loop:** `useVAD.js` records while speech is detected; after **3 seconds** of quiet it stops `MediaRecorder` and calls `processAudio(blob)`. Dashboard shows transcript + insight in `App.jsx`.
- **Caching:** Transformers.js uses the browser Cache API by default (not OPFS yet); large first download still only hits once per origin after cache is warm.

